---
kind: rule
version: "1.0"
name: nuget-cache
description: "Directs agents to the correct NuGet package cache location within the pixi environment."
activation: always
---
## NuGet Package Cache Location

The NuGet package cache is located inside the pixi environment, **not** in the user's home directory:

```
./.pixi/envs/default/var/cache/nuget
```

When looking for cached NuGet packages or .NET assemblies, inspect this path rather than `~/.nuget/packages`.
